data.description: Welcome home! This 3 bedroom, 1.5 bath home is located on just under a half an acre that is easy to maintain (20,909 sq. ft). Spacious living room with ductless heat pump & recessed lighting. Both bathrooms were updated with new tile and vanities. Kitchen with walk-in pantry & slider to covered back deck. All appliance stay including the washer & dryer. Storage/tool shed with dog kennel. Plenty of room for all your toys with oversized double car garage with workshop area plus a carport.
